version of this software as a network service — including the bundled web UI
(cmd/freeccrd) — you must offer its users access to the corresponding source
code.

No warranty; see sections 15–17 of the LICENSE.

Third-party components:
  - RAW decoding uses libraw (LGPL-2.1 / CDDL-1.0), linked at build time via
    cgo when built with `-tags libraw`. libraw is not distributed with this
    source; install it separately (e.g. `brew install libraw`).
  - Go standard library and golang.org/x/image (BSD-3-Clause).
